# edge_nodes.example
# Template for NSX Edge Node IP list.
#
# HOW TO USE:
#   cp edge_nodes.example edge_nodes.txt
#   Edit edge_nodes.txt with your real IPs.
#   edge_nodes.txt is git-ignored and will never be committed.
#
# FORMAT: one IPv4 address per line. Lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# Example:
# 192.168.10.10
# 192.168.10.11
# 192.168.10.12
